.dashboard-wrap
	.col-md-2
	.col-md-3
		.add-new-habit
			.new-habit-inner-container
				h3 Add a Habit
				a(href="/create")
					.add-icon
		.archived-habit-button
			h3 Archived Habits
			h1 0
	.col-md-5
		h1#habits-header Habits
		ul.habit(ng-repeat="habit in habits")
			li.habit-item 
				a(ng-click="analyzeHabit(habit)")
					h3 {{habit.name}}
				button.btn(ng-class="getButtonClass(habit.type)", ng-click="logHabit(habit)") {{getButtonText(habit.type)}}
		.no-habits(ng-hide="hasHabits()")
			| You are not tracking any habits.
	.col-md-2